    {
      "id": "PopularPost33541",
      "post_content": "Well, yes and no to it being better/worse than spearbreaker. Remember that basically vagrant plowbeasts picks up where spearbreaker leaves off. It can save your creatures from wither damage because regeneration removes all damage. Plus in the same way its giving regeneration to all your creatures, not only itself, and its colorless mana to regenerate rather than mono colored like you have in regular green or black. The multi colored aspect, while not such a big deal, also is beneficial like when using lieges or cards that reference only multi colored, or even one of the two like brave the elements. Spearbreaker is still technically better, but vagrant plowbeasts covers anything it misses.",
      "posted_by": "Donovan_Fabian",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost33541\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Well, yes and no to it being better/worse than spearbreaker.  Remember that basically vagrant plowbeasts picks up where spearbreaker leaves off.  It can save your creatures from wither damage because regeneration removes all damage.  Plus in the same way its giving regeneration to all your creatures, not only itself, and its colorless mana to regenerate rather than mono colored like you have in regular green or black.  The multi colored aspect, while not such a big deal, also is beneficial like when using lieges or cards that reference only multi colored, or even one of the two like brave the elements.  Spearbreaker is still technically better, but vagrant plowbeasts covers anything it misses.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '33541'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2942\">Donovan_Fabian</span>\r\n                                (11/4/2009 3:08:59 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_c